snippet.title: Gemini: Heroes Reborn coming soon to Xbox One
snippet.description: Combine superpowers like telekinesis and time travel and become the Hero, Cassandra. Use your skill and wits to battle her way through the enemy-filled secret facility, The Quarry, to save your abducted friend and solve a deep family mystery.
